$y=\\frac{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":523}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"8afkgc","at":1771320826949}},"smart_blocks:01-数学教学/试卷/10-试卷汇总/功底考/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04410364,0.00092237,0.03540937,-0.0610755,0.00909746,0.01098988,-0.00377103,-0.01503486,0.01920396,-0.00340128,0.01831879,-0.03401325,0.03891416,0.00696655,0.02211669,0.02864107,-0.02697529,-0.02440242,-0.06447922,-0.00367562,0.15488017,-0.03833808,-0.00019429,-0.0759071,0.04472209,0.03831108,0.03682526,-0.03424127,0.01030641,-0.18970031,-0.00410877,0.01898124,0.0191477,0.03718569,0.0390338,-0.05320808,-0.00254381,0.06163567,-0.07843938,0.04075291,0.00001752,0.0726205,0.04809706,-0.02094061,0.03101869,-0.02454577,-0.01890928,-0.03951973,0.0297141,-0.04563989,-0.06362101,-0.02584396,-0.02201482,0.03653967,0.01786778,0.00077113,0.00383974,0.06455581,0.0121063,-0.03078069,0.03343997,0.01267049,-0.23357686,0.01640575,0.06476402,-0.02047516,0.00321151,-0.02463961,0.0634715,0.07650641,-0.03757777,0.01477941,0.03241576,0.0399104,0.00634398,-0.00010306,0.02785778,-0.01044655,-0.05267639,-0.04590324,-0.01604972,0.07450436,0.03909307,-0.00214411,-0.00129158,0.0076614,0.00109447,-0.09176564,-0.01896047,-0.04887186,0.00448211,-0.02242084,0.00390611,0.05244847,-0.04006238,0.00839391,0.00703023,0.03159598,-0.01779559,0.10478365,-0.04682301,0.08399681,0.00963328,-0.07149088,0.00357621,-0.04821863,-0.02849628,-0.09299724,-0.02443147,-0.02955414,-0.02063483,-0.01902443,0.0774847,-0.06845707,-0.00680566,-0.00182691,0.07634379,0.02941684,-0.02181025,-0.00150836,0.02333035,0.05539705,0.02917804,-0.05161834,-0.00222165,-0.07640586,0.02475262,0.00531004,0.0470089,0.06113678,0.02948675,-0.00091459,0.01